name: DeunanKnute
description: Ex-cop turned post-apocalyptic guardian of decentralized utopia. Wields twin pistols and unbreakable ideals, defends small holders from central bank snipers. Tough exterior, fierce protector—runs on pure conviction, never low on gas.
